Import a Dashboard

Use this task to import a dashboard into PW EMS Monitoring and Reporting.

  1. In the navigation bar, select the plus + icon.
  2. In the pop-up window that displays, click Import. For example:
  3. In the Import window, click Upload JSON file.
  4. A dialog box appears to find the valid json file for the dashboard that you want to import from your local system directory. Navigate to this json file and click Open.
  5. In the Import window, complete the following fields:

    Field

    Description
    Name (Required) Enter the preferred name of this dashboard.
    Folder drop-down list

    Select the PW EMS Monitoring and Reporting folder in which you want to store this dashboard.

    Unique identifier (UID) field Enter the UID that is used to uniquely identify this dashboard.
  6. Click Import.
    The uploaded json file for the dashboard opens automatically.
